## 二、代码实现与解析

### 习题1：字符替换（防XSS基础逻辑）
```python
# 简单实现特殊字符转义
def xss_basic_filter(text):
    text = text.replace("<", "&lt;")
    text = text.replace(">", "&gt;")
    text = text.replace("'", "&#39;")
    text = text.replace('"', "&quot;")
    return text
# 测试恶意输入
payload = "<script>alert('XSS')</script>"
res = xss_basic_filter(payload)
print("原内容：", payload)
print("过滤后：", res)

### 习题2：危险关键词检测
# 匹配常见XSS危险关键词
danger_list = ["script", "alert", "onload", "onclick"]
user_input = input("请输入页面内容：")

flag = False
for word in danger_list:
    if word in user_input.lower():
        flag = True
        break
if flag:
    print("检测到恶意脚本，禁止提交")
else:
    print("内容提交成功")

